# Build outputs for the #649 Windows-Hello approval helper.
#
# Source-only in git (HelloVerify.csproj + Program.cs); the exe is built ON-BOX
# with `dotnet build -c Release -p:Platform=x64 tools/hello_verify`, exactly like
# the primary WinUI surface (services/ui_winui/bin is likewise uncommitted). The
# launcher resolves the Release exe by path and falls back cleanly if it is absent,
# so the binary never needs to live in the repo (and committing build artifacts is
# an anti-pattern — machine-generated, platform-specific, large).
bin/
obj/
